Business plan (includes 10 staff) → $119.99/mo
10 additional staff × $9 → $90/mo
Total: $119.99 + $90 = $219.99/mo

That $219.99/month includes scheduling, break enforcement, time tracking, overtime rules, PTO logic, leave approvals, multi-location compliance, payroll engine for US & Canada, W-2/T4/ROE file generation, Xero and QuickBooks exports, and branded booking + checkout.

